page.title: 01Wrentham Village
page.content: Wrentham is a village situated on the A 12 between Lowestoft and Ipswich. Although the population is relatively small there is a large number of small businesses. There is also a surprising range of activities both for adults and children. The village is likely to change in character when a by-pass is built diverting through- traffic away from the village centre. You will be able to find more about our village in the pages which follow. We have tried to write about things which we know about but which you might find difficult to find out about anywhere else.
